{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b1adcaab94","title":"致董必武等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f7ef1cf729","index":0,"year":1940,"month":11,"day":29,"articleId":"b1adcaab94"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji15","name":"毛泽东全集第15卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji15.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji15":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b070cd2490","type":"paragraph","text":"致董必武等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"b1adcaab94"},{"id":"bcef21a401","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年11月29日）董老，并告恩来、胡服、项英、德怀、克农“佳电”在各方面起了很好影响，我们应乘此时机更将“佳电泛散播。朱总号日致胡宗南电，胡感日有回电，态度顺好。我们派南汉宸日内去见胡宗南，作一番大解释工作。胡军及西安紧张气，可能大泄下去，进攻边区可能避免。但我各地军事准备仍不松，我们愈有准备，蒋愈不敢进攻，各办事处亦然。否则仍是笔险的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"b1adcaab94"},{"id":"3ee66840b2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"b1adcaab94"},{"id":"2839210394","type":"paragraph","text":"二十九日1这是毛泽东给董必武并告周题来、刘少奇、项英、彭德怀、李克农","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"b1adcaab94"}],"page":{"id":"cade40c6d0","publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"b1adcaab94","start":251,"end":251}}}},"__N_SSG":true}